    <title>0-总述</title>
    <url>/2026/06/07/%E5%B9%BF%E5%B7%9E%E5%9C%B0%E9%93%81/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="2026年粤港澳大湾区地铁轨道交通总数统计"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#2026年粤港澳大湾区地铁轨道交通总数统计"></a> 2026年粤港澳大湾区地铁（轨道交通）总数统计</h1>
<p>本统计数据更新至<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2026</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2026</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>年<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>月，统计范围为粤港澳大湾区<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>9</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">9</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">9</span></span></span></span>市<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span></span></span></span>区（广州、深圳、佛山、东莞、珠海、惠州、中山、江门、肇庆、香港、澳门），区分城市地铁（常规轨道交通）与城际轨道、有轨电车，核心统计大众日常通勤主流地铁线路，同步汇总全网总规模、运营里程与站点数量，清晰呈现“轨道上的大湾区”建设成果。</p>
<h2 id="一-大湾区地铁核心总览核心数据"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#一-大湾区地铁核心总览核心数据"></a> 一、大湾区地铁核心总览（核心数据）</h2>
<p>截至<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2026</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2026</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>年<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>月，粤港澳大湾区全域已运营轨道交通（含地铁、市域快线、轻轨、澳门轻轨、港铁主线）核心数据汇总：</p>
<ul>
<li>总运营线路数：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>90</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">90</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">9</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>条</li>
<li>总运营站点数：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>1704</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1704</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">7</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">4</span></span></span></span>座</li>
<li>全域轨道交通总里程：突破<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2800</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2800</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">8</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>公里</li>
<li>核心城市地铁覆盖率：广深佛莞四大核心城市实现全域主城区地铁覆盖，形成大湾区一小时通勤轨道网络</li>
</ul>
<p>注：数据不含单独统计的有轨电车支线、景区捷运、市内微循环小轨道，仅统计对外公共通勤主干轨道交通线路。</p>
<h2 id="二-各城市地铁运营明细2026最新"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#二-各城市地铁运营明细2026最新"></a> 二、各城市地铁运营明细（2026最新）</h2>
<h3 id="1-广州市"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#1-广州市"></a> 1. 广州市</h3>
<p>作为大湾区轨道枢纽核心，广州地铁线网规模稳居全国前列。目前已运营<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>19</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">19</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">9</span></span></span></span>条地铁主干线路，不含支线拆分统计，全网运营总里程<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>779</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">779</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">7</span><span class="mord">7</span><span class="mord">9</span></span></span></span>公里，运营车站<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>398</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">398</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">3</span><span class="mord">9</span><span class="mord">8</span></span></span></span>座。<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2026</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2026</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>年持续推进<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>15</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">15</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">5</span></span></span></span>条、<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>361</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">361</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">3</span><span class="mord">6</span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span>公里轨道交通建设，年内计划开通<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>条（段）地铁、<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">4</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">4</span></span></span></span>条城际线路，进一步加密中心城区与外围城区轨道衔接。</p>
<h3 id="2-深圳市"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#2-深圳市"></a> 2. 深圳市</h3>
<p>深圳地铁高速扩容，当前已运营<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>16</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">16</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>条地铁主干线路，另有<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span>条线路即将通车，同步配套<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span></span></span></span>条有轨电车线路。<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2026</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2026</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>年深圳重点推进<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>11</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">11</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span>条城市轨道线路建设，全域地铁站点<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>800</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">800</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">8</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>米覆盖率超<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>85</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">85\%</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.80556em;vertical-align:-0.05556em;"></span><span class="mord">8</span><span class="mord">5</span><span class="mord">%</span></span></span></span>，核心区轨道密度位居大湾区首位，形成全覆盖、高时效的都市圈轨道网络。</p>
<h3 id="3-佛山市"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#3-佛山市"></a> 3. 佛山市</h3>
<p>佛山依托广佛同城优势，轨道全面对接广州线网，是大湾区跨城地铁互通最成熟的城市。目前已运营多条跨城及市域地铁线路，全面融入广州轨道网络，实现广佛核心区无缝换乘，助力大湾区同城化发展。</p>
<h3 id="4-东莞市"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#4-东莞市"></a> 4. 东莞市</h3>
<p>东莞聚焦临深、临广轨道衔接，当前已运营主干地铁线路，另有多条市域地铁、跨城城际轨道在建，串联广州、深圳核心城区，是大湾区中部轨道通勤的重要枢纽节点。</p>
<h3 id="5-香港特别行政区"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#5-香港特别行政区"></a> 5. 香港特别行政区</h3>
<p>香港轨道体系成熟完善，港铁主干运营线路<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>10</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">10</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>条，配套<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>12</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">12</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">2</span></span></span></span>条轻铁线路、<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>条叮叮车线路及<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">3</span></span></span></span>条机场捷运线路，公共轨道出行覆盖率极高，是大湾区轨道交通运营效率最高的区域之一。</p>
<h3 id="6-澳门特别行政区"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#6-澳门特别行政区"></a> 6. 澳门特别行政区</h3>
<p>澳门当前运营<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span>条轻轨线路，另有<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">3</span></span></span></span>条轻轨线路规划在建，逐步完善澳门本地轨道网络，同时对接大湾区内地城市轨道体系。</p>
<h3 id="7-珠海-惠州-中山-江门-肇庆"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#7-珠海-惠州-中山-江门-肇庆"></a> 7. 珠海、惠州、中山、江门、肇庆</h3>
<p>上述五市现阶段以城际轨道交通为主要通勤轨道，暂无成熟运营的城市主干地铁线路，目前多条城际轨道、市域快轨在建及规划中，逐步接入大湾区整体轨道网络。</p>
<h2 id="三-大湾区轨道网络整体格局"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#三-大湾区轨道网络整体格局"></a> 三、大湾区轨道网络整体格局</h2>
<p>当前粤港澳大湾区已形成“广深双核引领、佛莞联动、全域互通”的轨道交通格局。通过地铁、市域快线、城际铁路多网融合，实现广、深、佛、莞四城地铁无缝换乘，搭配全域<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>90</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">90</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">9</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>条轨道线路、<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>1704</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1704</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">7</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">4</span></span></span></span>座站点、超<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2800</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2800</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">8</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>公里的运营里程，全面成型大湾区一小时通勤生活圈。</p>
<p>根据远期规划，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2030</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2030</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">3</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>年大湾区轨道交通线路将扩容至<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>110</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">110</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>条、<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2121</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2121</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span>座站点，轨道网络覆盖密度、跨城通行效率将进一步提升，全面支撑粤港澳大湾区一体化发展。</p>
<h2 id="四-统计说明"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#四-统计说明"></a> 四、统计说明</h2>
<ol>
<li>统计时间：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2026</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2026</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>年<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>月，包含年内已开通新线，不含未通车在建、规划线路；</li>
<li>统计口径：主干地铁、市域快线、港澳主干轨道、澳门轻轨，剔除小众微循环轨道、景区专线、单独有轨电车支线；</li>
<li>数据来源：广州地铁、深圳地铁官方发布、广东省轨道交通建设公示、大湾区轨道行业权威统计。</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
