    <title>广州地铁1号线</title>
    <url>/2026/06/09/%E5%B9%BF%E5%B7%9E%E5%9C%B0%E9%93%811%E5%8F%B7%E7%BA%BF/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="广州地铁1号线介绍"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#广州地铁1号线介绍"></a> 广州地铁1号线介绍</h1>
<p>广州地铁1号线是广州市首条建成运营的城市轨道交通线路，也是大湾区早期核心通勤干线，代表色为<strong>黄色</strong>。</p>
<h2 id="一-基本概况"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#一-基本概况"></a> 一、基本概况</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>开通时间</strong>：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>1997</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1997</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">9</span><span class="mord">9</span><span class="mord">7</span></span></span></span>年<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>月<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>28</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">28</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">8</span></span></span></span>日首段（西塱—黄沙）观光试运营，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>1999</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1999</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">9</span><span class="mord">9</span><span class="mord">9</span></span></span></span>年<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>月<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>28</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">28</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">8</span></span></span></span>日全线正式运营。</li>
<li><strong>线路走向</strong>：西南—东北走向，起于荔湾区<strong>西塱站</strong>，止于天河区<strong>广州东站</strong>，途经荔湾、越秀、天河三区。</li>
<li><strong>线路长度</strong>：全长<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>18.497</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">18.497</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">8</span><span class="mord">.</span><span class="mord">4</span><span class="mord">9</span><span class="mord">7</span></span></span></span>千米，其中地下段<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>16.449</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">16.449</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">6</span><span class="mord">.</span><span class="mord">4</span><span class="mord">4</span><span class="mord">9</span></span></span></span>千米、地面段<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2.048</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2.048</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">.</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">4</span><span class="mord">8</span></span></span></span>千米。</li>
<li><strong>车站数量</strong>：共设<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>16</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">16</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>座车站，含西塱、坑口<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span></span></span></span>座地面站，其余为地下站。</li>
<li><strong>列车编组</strong>：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>节编组A型列车。</li>
<li><strong>客流强度</strong>：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2024</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2024</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">4</span></span></span></span>年日均客流<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>83.43</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">83.43</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">8</span><span class="mord">3</span><span class="mord">.</span><span class="mord">4</span><span class="mord">3</span></span></span></span>万人次，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2025</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2025</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">5</span></span></span></span>年稳居全国地铁单线客流强度首位。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="二-运营信息2026最新"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#二-运营信息2026最新"></a> 二、运营信息（2026最新）</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>首末班车</strong>：
<ul>
<li>西塱→广州东站：首班<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>06</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>00</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">06:00</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">6</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>，末班<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>22</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>55</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">22:55</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">5</span><span class="mord">5</span></span></span></span></li>
<li>广州东站→西塱：首班<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>06</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">06:10</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">6</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>，末班<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>23</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>30</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">23:30</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">3</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">3</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>发车间隔</strong>：平峰约<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">4</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">4</span></span></span></span>分钟，高峰加密班次。</li>
<li><strong>票价范围</strong>：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span></span></span></span>–<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>5</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">5</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">5</span></span></span></span>元。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="三-站点与换乘16站"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#三-站点与换乘16站"></a> 三、站点与换乘（16站）</h2>
<ol>
<li>西塱（换乘广佛线、<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>10</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">10</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>号线、<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>22</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">22</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">2</span></span></span></span>号线）</li>
<li>坑口</li>
<li>花地湾</li>
<li>芳村（换乘<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>11</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">11</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span>号线、<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>22</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">22</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">2</span></span></span></span>号线）</li>
<li>黄沙（换乘<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>号线）</li>
<li>长寿路</li>
